Sarah Perry, <a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780063352612" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>Enlightenment</em></a><br />
Kiley Reid, <a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780593328200" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>Come and Get It</em></a><br />
Rebecca K. Reilly, <a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9781668028049" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>Greta &amp; Valdin</em></a><br />
Aaron Robertson, <a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780374604981" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>The Black Utopians</em></a><br />
Cat Sebastian, <a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780063272804" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>You Should Be So Lucky</em></a><br />
Francis Spufford, <a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9781668025451" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>Cahokia Jazz</em></a><br />
Rufi Thorpe, <a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780063356580" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>Margo&#8217;s Got Money Troubles</em></a><br />
Mosab Abu Toha, <a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780593803974" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>Forest of Noise</em></a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">*</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>List of Lists Surveyed:</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">TIME&#8217;s <a href="https://time.com/collection/must-read-books-2024/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">100 Must-Read Books of 2024</a>  and <a href="https://time.com/7199834/best-fiction-books-2024/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">10 Best Fiction Books of 2024</a> and <a href="https://time.com/7200389/best-nonfiction-books-2024/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">10 Best Nonfiction Books of 2024</a> • Publishers Weekly&#8217;s <a href="https://best-books.publishersweekly.com/pw/best-books/2024" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best Books of 2024</a> • <em>Vanity Fair&#8217;s</em> <a href="https://www.vanityfair.com/style/story/best-books-2024" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">21 Best Books of 2024 to Read Right Now</a> • <em>The Economist&#8217;s</em> <a href="https://www.economist.com/culture/2024/11/22/the-best-books-of-2024-as-chosen-by-the-economist" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best Books of 2024</a> • <em>The New York Times&#8217;</em> <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2024/11/26/books/notable-books.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">100 Notable Books of 2024</a> and <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2024/12/03/books/best-books-2024.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">10 Best Books of 2024</a> • <em>The Washington Post&#8217;s</em> <a href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/books/2024/11/21/best-fiction/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">50 Notable Works of Fiction from 2024</a> and <a href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/books/2024/11/21/best-nonfiction/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">50 Notable Works of Nonfiction from 2024</a> and <a href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/books/2024/11/22/10-best-books/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">10 Best Books of 2024</a> • Kirkus Reviews&#8217; <a href="https://www.kirkusreviews.com/best-of/2024/fiction/books/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best Fiction Books of the Year</a> and <a href="https://www.kirkusreviews.com/best-of/2024/nonfiction/books/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best Nonfiction Books of the Year</a> • <em>The Globe and Mail&#8217;s</em> <a href="https://www.theglobeandmail.com/arts/books/article-the-globe-100-the-best-books-of-2024/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">100 Best Books of 2024</a> • <em>The Chicago Tribune&#8217;s</em> <a href="https://www.chicagotribune.com/2024/11/26/best-books-2024/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">10 Best Books of 2024</a> • Den of Geek&#8217;s <a href="https://www.denofgeek.com/books/den-of-geeks-best-books-of-2024/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best Books of 2024</a> • <em>The Times&#8217;</em> <a href="https://www.thetimes.com/culture/books/article/best-fiction-books-2024-tdzhd5x0n?region=global" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">18 Best Novels of 2024</a> and <a href="https://www.thetimes.com/culture/books/article/best-history-books-2024-wl350lcf9?region=global" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">21 Best History Books of 2024</a> and <a href="https://www.thetimes.com/culture/books/article/best-history-books-2024-wl350lcf9?region=global" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">8 Best Thought and Ideas Books of 2024</a> and <a href="https://www.thetimes.com/culture/books/article/best-literary-non-fiction-books-2024-tm5fg86d0?region=global" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">9 Best Literary Nonfiction Books of 2024</a> and <a href="https://www.thetimes.com/culture/books/article/best-political-books-2024-nnjf5gx7k?region=global" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">9 Best Politics Books of 2024</a> and <a href="https://www.thetimes.com/culture/books/article/best-crime-mystery-books-2024-23nvchtfj?region=global" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">10 Best Crime Books of 2024</a> and <a href="https://www.thetimes.com/culture/books/article/best-thriller-books-2024-dvckcfpvc" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">10 Best Thrillers of 2024</a> and <a href="https://www.thetimes.com/culture/books/article/best-historical-fiction-of-2024-so-far-j8vzbqbq7?region=global" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">10 Best Historical Fiction Books of 2024</a> and <a href="https://www.thetimes.com/culture/books/article/best-biographies-books-2024-pzhdww8t2?region=global" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">10 Best Biographies and Memoirs of 2024</a> • BookRiot&#8217;s <a href="https://bookriot.com/best-books-2024/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best Books of 2024</a> • The NYPL&#8217;s <a href="https://www.nypl.org/books-more/recommendations/best-books/adults?year=2024" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best Books for Adults 2024</a> • <em>The Telegraph&#8217;s</em> <a href="https://www.telegraph.co.uk/books/what-to-read/what-books-to-buy-christmas-best-books-2024-ranked/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">50 Best Books of 2024, Ranked</a> • The New Statesman&#8217;s <a href="https://www.newstatesman.com/culture/books/2024/11/best-books-year-2024" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Books of the Year 2024</a> • The Chicago Public Library&#8217;s <a href="https://chipublib.bibliocommons.com/v2/list/display/199702383/2654278837" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Favorite Books of 2024</a> • NPR&#8217;s <a href="https://apps.npr.org/best-books/#tags=staff+picks&amp;view=covers&amp;year=2024" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Books We Love (Staff Picks)</a> • <em>The Independent&#8217;s</em> <a href="https://www.the-independent.com/arts-entertainment/books/features/best-fiction-books-2024-rooney-ohagen-headshot-b2616300.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best Fiction Books of 2024</a> and <a href="https://www.the-independent.com/arts-entertainment/books/features/best-non-fiction-books-2024-true-crime-b2651350.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best Nonfiction Books of 2024</a> • Amazon Books Editors&#8217; <a href="https://www.aboutamazon.com/news/books-and-authors/best-books-amazon-2024" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best Books of 2024</a> • Hudson Booksellers&#8217; <a href="https://www.hudsonbooksellers.com/best-books-2024" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best Books of 2024</a> • Barnes &amp; Noble&#8217;s <a href="https://www.barnesandnoble.com/b/books/barnes-nobles-best-books-of-2024/barnes-nobles-best-fiction-of-2024/_/N-29Z8q8Z30qr" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best Fiction of 2024</a> and <a href="https://www.barnesandnoble.com/b/books/barnes-nobles-best-books-of-2024/barnes-nobles-best-mystery-thriller-books-of-2024/_/N-29Z8q8Z30qu" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best Mystery and Thrillers of 2024</a> and<a href="https://www.barnesandnoble.com/b/books/barnes-nobles-best-books-of-2024/barnes-nobles-best-science-fiction-fantasy-books-of-2024/_/N-29Z8q8Z30t3" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"> Best Science Fiction and Fantasy Books of 2024</a> and <a href="https://www.barnesandnoble.com/b/books/barnes-nobles-best-books-of-2024/barnes-nobles-best-history-books-of-2024/_/N-29Z8q8Z30t5" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best History Books of 2024</a> and <a href="https://www.barnesandnoble.com/b/books/barnes-nobles-best-books-of-2024/barnes-nobles-best-memoirs-of-2024/_/N-29Z8q8Z30t8" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best Biography and Memoir of 2024</a> and <a href="https://www.barnesandnoble.com/b/books/barnes-nobles-best-books-of-2024/barnes-nobles-best-smart-thinking-books-of-2024/_/N-29Z8q8Z30t9" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best Smart Thinking Books of 2024</a> • Vulture&#8217;s <a href="https://www.vulture.com/article/best-books-2024-new-novels-fiction.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best Books of 2024</a> • <em>The Atlantic&#8217;s</em> <a href="https://www.theatlantic.com/books/archive/2024/12/best-books-2024-percival-everett-alexei-navalny/680729/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">10 Best Books of 2024</a> • <em>ELLE&#8217;s</em> <a href="https://www.elle.com/culture/books/g63073207/editor-picks-best-books-2024/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Editors Recommend Their Favorite Books of 2024</a> • BookPage&#8217;s <a href="https://www.bookpage.com/best-books/best-nonfiction/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best Nonfiction of 2024</a> and <a href="https://www.bookpage.com/best-books/best-fiction/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best Fiction of 2024</a> • Electric Lit&#8217;s <a href="https://electricliterature.com/electric-lits-best-novels-of-2024/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best Novels of 2024</a> and <a href="https://electricliterature.com/electric-lits-best-nonfiction-of-2024/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best Nonfiction of 2024</a> and <a href="https://electricliterature.com/electric-lits-best-poetry-collections-of-2024/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best Poetry Collections of 2024</a> and <a href="https://electricliterature.com/electric-lits-best-short-story-collections-of-2024/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best Short Story Collections of 2024</a> • Vox&#8217;s <a href="https://www.vox.com/culture/389984/best-books-2024-martyr-kaveh-akbar-small-rain-garth-greenwell" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best Books of 2024</a> • <em>The Wall Street Journal&#8217;s </em><a href="https://www.wsj.com/arts-culture/books/the-10-best-books-of-2024-b67ada25" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">10 Best Books of 2024</a> • <em>The New Yorker&#8217;s</em> <a href="https://www.newyorker.com/best-books-2024" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best Books of 2024 (Essential Reads)</a> • Library Journal&#8217;s <a href="https://www.libraryjournal.com/story/Best-Nonfiction-2024" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best Nonfiction of 2024</a> and <a href="https://www.libraryjournal.com/story/Reviews%2B/Best-Literary-Fiction-2024" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best Literary Fiction of 2024</a> and <a href="https://www.libraryjournal.com/story/related/Best-Poetry-2024" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best Poetry of 2024</a> and <a href="https://www.libraryjournal.com/story/Best-Pop-Fiction-2024" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best Pop Fiction of 2024</a> and <a href="https://www.libraryjournal.com/story/related/Best-Crime-Fiction-2024" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best Crime Fiction of 2024</a> and <a href="https://www.libraryjournal.com/story/related/Best-Science-Fiction-and-Fantasy-2024" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best Science Fiction and Fantasy 2024</a> and <a href="https://www.libraryjournal.com/story/related/Best-Horror-2024" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best Horror of 2024</a> and <a href="https://www.libraryjournal.com/story/Best-Graphic-Novels-2024" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best Graphic Novels of 2024</a> and <a href="https://www.libraryjournal.com/story/related/Best-Romance-Fiction-2024" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best Romance of 2024</a> • <em>The Guardian&#8217;s</em> <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/books/2024/dec/07/the-best-books-of-2024" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best Books of 2024</a> • <em>PEOPLE&#8217;s </em><a href="https://people.com/people-picks-the-top-10-books-of-2024-8757019" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">10 Best Books of 2024</a> • Slate&#8217;s <a href="https://slate.com/culture/2024/12/best-books-2024-novels-nonfiction-fantasy-science-fiction.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">10 Best Books of 2024 (Kois)</a> and <a href="https://slate.com/culture/2024/12/best-books-2024-nonfiction-novels.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">10 Best Books of 2024 (Miller)</a> • <em>The LA Times&#8217;s </em><a href="https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/story/2024-12-10/best-books-of-2024-reissues-included" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">15 Best Books of 2024</a> • <em>Oprah</em> Daily&#8217;s <a href="https://www.oprahdaily.com/entertainment/books/a62969406/best-books-2024/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best Books of 2024</a> • and of course, Literary Hub&#8217;s <a href="https://lithub.com/lit-hubs-38-favorite-books-of-2024/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Favorite Books of 2024</a>.</p>
										
																				
																		
